      value: ...maybe you could change that.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2913163817265418663, guid: f26c40c74954afb4d9de004927a5ba54, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogue1.Array.data[4]'
      value: It's up to you. Do you want to be a star worker, or do you want to consider
        the greater good?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2913163817265418663, guid: f26c40c74954afb4d9de004927a5ba54, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogue1.Array.data[5]'
      value: To make changes or read the messages, click their icons in the top left.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2913163817265418663, guid: f26c40c74954afb4d9de004927a5ba54, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogue1.Array.data[6]'
      value: Anyway, I heard that the key was somewhere down the hallway the way
        you came. Good luck finding it!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2913163817265418663, guid: f26c40c74954afb4d9de004927a5ba54, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogue2.Array.data[0]'
